data.description:
Welcome to this charming home featuring 3 bedrooms, 1 bath, and an inviting front porch. Boasting 1290 square feet, the interior showcases stylish LVT flooring that spans the entire space. Enjoy the recently updated bathroom, adding a modern touch to this classic residence.

The generously sized bedrooms offer ample space for relaxation and personalization, ensuring comfort for everyone in the household. The convenient laundry area is situated under the attached carport for added practicality.

With its thoughtful design and updates, this home combines style and functionality. Explore every corner of this home with the 3D Virtual Tour, allowing you to envision the possibilities from the comfort of your own space. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming residence your own – schedule a viewing today!
